One important=C2=A0but not necessarily permanent=C2=A0lesson of the Year of=
 Meme Stocks is that if you run a public company you should try to meme it =
up as much as possible, because your job is to create shareholder value and=
 doing meme stuff creates shareholder value. Exactly what constitutes =E2=
=80=9Cdoing meme stuff=E2=80=9D depends on what memes are popular in any gi=
ven week, but broadly speaking talking about electric cars or cryptocurrenc=
ies or non-fungible tokens or Elon Musk or=C2=A0other=C2=A0meme stocks is u=
sually a decent way to get attention and have your stock go up. Being on Tw=
itter or Reddit a lot, using the right slang and the right emojis, generall=
y conveying to retail investors that you are in on the joke, these things b=
uild shareholder loyalty and can cause your stock to [rocket emoji].All of =
this stuff is pretty much unrelated to actual business results; my point he=
re is not =E2=80=9Cif you sell non-fungible tokens and they bring in hundre=
ds of millions of dollars investors will put an attractive multiple on thos=
e earnings=E2=80=9D but rather =E2=80=9Cif you say =E2=80=98NFT=E2=80=99 on=
 a conference call your stock will go up.=E2=80=9D Last Thursday  Netflix I=
nc. announced disappointing subscriber growth numbers, and  the stock tanke=
d. On Friday, Netflix Engineering tweeted: =E2=80=9CWhat are your thoughts =
on NFTs?=E2=80=9D=C2=A0I love it, but it did not work at all. The stock was=
 down 21.8% on the day, with no noticeable reaction to the midday NFT tweet=
; it was down further this morning. This is bad news for Netflix but I pref=
er to focus on the positive, which is that it is very good news for all of =
the public company CEOs who do not personally want=C2=A0to go around talkin=
g about NFTs all the time. As of December it looked like their fiduciary du=
ties to shareholders might require them to do NFTs whether they want to or =
not.=C2=A0Now they don=E2=80=99t have to! Going on Twitter to say =E2=80=9C=
NFTs=E2=80=9D doesn=E2=80=99t work anymore! The magic is gone! You can go b=
ack to running your business instead of doing meme stuff; everything is nor=
mal again.
