olutely normal.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I don=E2=80=99t wa=
nt to say that that was=C2=A0<em>right </em>=E2=80=94=C2=A0honestly I was k=
idding =E2=80=94=C2=A0but I do feel a little bit like people are celebratin=
g the anniversary of the meme stock boom by declaring that it=E2=80=99s ove=
r? For instance, here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/26470748.263630/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud3NqLmNvbS9hcnRpY2xlcy9yZWRkaXRzLXdh=
