 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> couple</a> of <a href=3D"ht=
tps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26470748.263630/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3c=
uYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDctMDIvcm9iaW5ob29kLWlwby=
1maWxpbmctaXMtYS1sZXNzb24taW4tbWVtZS1maW5hbmNlP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMjQyMl9NT05FW=
VNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIy=
